name: escalate-inline-or-plan
summary: 'Size a work-shaped request to choose where it lands: inline (1-2 files, no new contracts, wanted now), /plan:plan (multi-module or new contract or 3+ moves), or /plan:defer (inline-shaped but not now). Tie-break toward plan over inline, defer over now.'
domain: engineering
